#Tree move- unlock for 10 wood, 10 pinecones, 10 bananas. Removes tree from map and makes it a placable item in inventory. #Banish- unlock by having 9 neighbors with houses. Forces instant neighbor move out and removes their home from the island. #Transmute- unlocked by having more than 50 of an item. Allows player to transform 10 of an item into 3 of a different item.# Teleport- Unlock through "Mubabas quest". Allows player to warp between worlds without using portals. 